### Tool 列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tools

### AI 聊天（SSE 流式 + Tool Calling）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "Calculate the area of a rectangle 3 meters by 4 meters.",
  "enableTools": true
}

### AI 聊天（仅流式，不启用 Tool）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "Hello",
  "enableTools": false
}

### RAG 流式问答
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "question": "What is the refund policy?",
  "topK": 3,
  "enableTools": true
}

### 预期 SSE 事件序列（示例）
# data: {"type":"start","conversationId":"...","timestamp":...}
# data: {"type":"chunk","content":"..."}
# data: {"type":"tool_call","toolId":"...","toolName":"calculateArea","arguments":{...}}
# data: {"type":"tool_result","toolId":"...","toolName":"calculateArea","success":true,"result":"12.00"}
# data: {"type":"done","durationMs":...}
